MANAGE YOUR eSIM
NEXTCARE
care@nextsim.travel
+27 686 428 000
1. Make sure you 're connected to the Internet and have your Next eSIM email ready.
2. Go to settings >Connections >Sim Manager >add eSIM.
3. Scan the eSIM QR code from your Next eSIM email or select photo gallery at bottom
of screen and choose a snapshot of it
4. Enable your new eSIM and rename by tapping on it for easy identification
5. InstallNext Internet Settings: Go to Settings >Connections >Mobile networks >
Access point name.
6. Select your new eSIM at the bottom and Tap the add icon (or 3 dots).
7. Name your APN “Next” and for APN, enter “next.movedata.mobi ” and save.
8. Choose this new “Next” APN for your new eSIM and enable data roaming.
You 're all set! To use your new Next eSIM while traveling, go to Settings >Connections >
sim manager and under preferred sim select the new eSIM for calls and mobile data.
Then switch off data switching.
Android Devices
1. Make sure you 're connected to the Internet and have your Next eSIM email ready.
2. Go to Settings >Mobile Data.
3. Add eSIM and choose'Use QR Code ' for setup.
4. Option 1: Scan the QR code from your printed eSIM email or another device screen
Option 2: if not possible, select ‘enter details manually’and copy and paste the
‘SM-DP+Address’ and ‘Activation Code’ from your Next eSIM email.
5. Switch on your new eSIM and enable data roaming for the new eSIM
6. Install Next Internet settings using this link:
https://p.move-iot-connect.com/nextcellular . Then Go to Settings >Profile
Downloaded >Install >Next >Install.
You 're all set!To use your new Next eSIM while traveling, go to Settings > Mobile
Dataand select the new eSIM for mobile data and your default voice line.
